org.matsim.contrib.socnetsim.framework.replanning.grouping

Class GroupPlans

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.contrib.socnetsim.framework.replanning.grouping.GroupPlans

  • public class GroupPlans
extends Object
    Stores plans for a group. For plans pertaining to a joint plan, the joint plan is stored; for individual plans, the individual plan is stored.
    The collections returned are the interal references. GroupStrategyModules may modify them if needed.
    Author:
    thibautd
